{"title":"三体","time_limit":250,"memory_limit":512,"tags":["2020小学期"],"operation":{"submit":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/problem/1212#submit_code","submissions":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/submissions?problem_id=1212","statistics":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/problem/1212/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/problem/1212/testdata","discussion":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/discussion/problem/1212"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"有三个同心圆，每个同心圆上随机分布了一个点，以均匀的概率出现。你需要求出三个点组成三角形的期望大小。\r\n\r\n时间限制=250ms"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"一行一个整数，$n$\r\n接下来 $n$ 行，每行三个整数 $r_1,r_2,r_3 $，代表三个圆的半径。"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"每行一个实数，代表答案。"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"#### 样例输入\r\n```\r\n10\r\n1 1 1\r\n1 2 3\r\n2 3 4\r\n3 4 5\r\n4 5 6\r\n5 6 7\r\n6 7 8\r\n7 8 9\r\n8 9 10\r\n9 10 11\r\n```\r\n#### 样例输出\r\n```\r\n0.477464829279533\r\n2.082911838942238\r\n4.485629669048650\r\n7.839840108875121\r\n12.146357503569837\r\n17.405953684319137\r\n23.619148249366535\r\n30.786285875067207\r\n38.907601047328640\r\n47.983258241109496\r\n```"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"$n \\le 1000, 1 \\le r_1,r_2,r_3 \\le 1000$\r\n\r\n如果你的答案绝对误差或相对误差小于 $10^{-8}$ ，则可以通过此题。"}]}